{"tid":1506414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我同你地講香港一定要獨立，我地係香港人","createTime":"2019-08-25T19:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:47:06.000Z","uid":150079,"like":216,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"6895d3cd20dd4e0e7c09c227d46972595d3cab98","tid":1506414,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:34:17.000Z","msg":"因為外國人根本當香港係中國<br />\n我哋做咗奴隸20年，你唔係覺得冇問題啊？<br />\n有時候日本人當我係日本人<br />\n始終我都會答佢係香港人<br />\n我唔係日本人，但佢地當香港係中國<br />\n我同你地講香港嘅時候我喊咗好多次，<br />\n唔該你哋啦唔好再支持一國兩制，中共信唔過<br />\n一日中國香港，一日中國人"},{"pid":"a0fe6bbd91e0530d0b1c2514832b5c4e794219c3","tid":1506414,"uid":207476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:35:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0d05cc9a49ca2eec038a996dd2328b4ee45e76a1","tid":1506414,"uid":22675,"like":36,"dislike":4,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:35:54.000Z","msg":"我好嬲，下次出嚟我要嗌香港獨立，唔再叫時代革命"},{"pid":"c805a316453e76431b8dde0076b9db82b4e3dbc9","tid":1506414,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:21:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c578b2566cdc3ecf7be532d41582f1443a8c3c5","tid":1506414,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:21:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"378f8b9f67c384fe8077055308adfc8172d5292c","tid":1506414,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:21:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e2bc6de43a087cedc85a2890b69e80cbfc1e473","tid":1506414,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:26:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c44e5c193545721182e85d1779594f1403760121","tid":1506414,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:27:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba193da2d6b0e9017b21e843540075f9bf7775a4","tid":1506414,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:32:36.000Z","msg":"[突發]撐狗學生寫左封信比人民日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1